SCENE Contributor Covenant

We welcome contributors who are committed to:
	•	Abolitionist values, racial equity, and digital dignity.
	•	Protecting the lives and voices of formerly incarcerated and marginalized communities.
	•	Participating in community dialogue around safety and impact.

As a contributor, you agree to:
	•	Communicate with respect and humility.
	•	Prioritize the lived experiences of system-impacted individuals.
	•	Document your contributions with transparency.
	•	Never use this project for oppressive, exploitative, or surveillance-related efforts